 "title": "Sticky chicken – hard to translate (klewerige/taai hoender)",
 "excerpt": "I was in the mood for lovely sticky, lick-your-fingers, syrupy chicken. You'll need to wash your mouth and hands after eating this. You can cut back on the sugar if you don't want something quite so sweet. INGREDIENTS: 1 cup tomato sauce 1 cup brown sugar 1 cup honey 1/2 cup soy sauce 4 cloves of garlic NOW: …",
